WEBVTT

00:08:01.208 --> 00:08:02.409
Jo, nuk munden.

00:08:02.433 --> 00:08:05.909
(Te qeshura) (Duartrokitje)

00:08:05.933 --> 00:08:07.480
Keshtu tani ju mund te pyesni

00:08:08.504 --> 00:08:12.136
pse genjeshtrat e femijeve 
jane kaq te veshtira per t'u dalluar.

00:08:12.958 --> 00:08:15.970
Me lejoni ta ilustroj kete
me djalin tim, Nathan.

00:08:15.994 --> 00:08:18.163
Kjo eshte mimika e tij

00:08:18.187 --> 00:08:19.571
kur genjen.

00:08:19.595 --> 00:08:21.801
(Te qeshura)

00:08:21.825 --> 00:08:23.427
Keshtu kur femijet genjejne,

00:08:23.451 --> 00:08:26.607
mimika e tyre eshte zakonisht neutrale.

00:08:27.123 --> 00:08:30.583
Sidoqofte, pas kesaj pamje neurale,